  "texts": [
    "Therefore, the TFT hyperparameters are tuned using Optuna.Neural Basis Expansion Analysis for Time Series Forecasting (N-Beats): N-Beats uses a stack of fully connected blocks, where each block learns to model either trend or seasonality.",
    "Each block contains a backcast output, which reconstructs the input, and a forecast output, which predicts future values.",
    "The key innovation in N-Beats is this backcast-forecast structure, which allows the model to correct errors over layers and refine its predictions.",
    "Unlike models that rely on recurrence or convolutions, N-Beats uses only feedforward layers, making it fast and easy to train while still capturing complex patterns.",
    "We implement N-Beats and hyperparameter tuning using PyTorch Forecasting as well."
  ],
  "correct_citations": []
}